      • getLevelInfo

        @Query(value=" WITH RECURSIVE levels_cte(id, label, parent_id, depth,team_id) AS( SELECT tn.id, tn.label, tn.parent_id , CAST(\'1\' AS INTEGER) AS depth,CAST(tn.id AS INTEGER) AS team_id FROM level_hierarchy AS tn  WHERE tn.parent_id = 0UNION ALL SELECT c.id, c.label, c.parent_id, p.depth + 1 AS depth,        (p.team_id) FROM levels_cte AS p, level_hierarchy AS c  WHERE c.parent_id = p.id)SELECT * FROM levels_cte AS n WHERE n.label = :levelName AND n.team_id=    (SELECT t.id FROM level_hierarchy AS t WHERE t.label=:teamName )",
       nativeQuery=true)
